{"tid":1641290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"call g奶hi時奶到粒軟野出來, 食咗屎嘅機會有幾大?","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:31:45.000Z","uid":76115,"like":13,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9dbc242166b9e2e7ca53df23dfa6a071cfb420","tid":1641290,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"佢是陀地骨妹來, 貪佢夠後生+幾大波+享受食mk妹滋味成日幫襯, 但佢啲頭髮好能鞋同間唔中有白色珍珠口臭, 應該唔太重個人衛生<br />\n尋晚佢主動提議奶, 我盛情難卻就奶下佢, 咁我本身從未奶過但又想扮勁, 所以成個閪+近屎眼位置含哂落口, 又扮av男傻整啲飲湯雪雪雪咁嘅聲出來<br />\nso far so good, 點知奶到咁上下感覺到有成粒軟野甩咗出來喺個口到, 條脷喺幾秒間feel到個觸感似係食完肉無撩牙隔一陣自己跌出來個啲渣<br />\n雖然覺得核突但毒撚最驚hurt到人, 唔想吐返來, 掙扎咗一陣終於成粒連水吞咗落肚<br />\n個刻覺得無乜野, 呢兩日諗返先至覺得囉囉亂, 其實我係咪食咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041e9ac249448112abd8e969077f3ab4f6c3afcd","tid":1641290,"uid":205928,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"樓主講啲咁嘅嘢可唔可以轉台先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb582d7e4286504b1b855617821f15d9dd180ed","tid":1641290,"uid":34368,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"椰菜花"},{"pid":"f63bb5447b92e22b5b40000039f0ad9811dcef08","tid":1641290,"uid":211347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7965e153d9da97e6ece6dc723040d141bb0b72","tid":1641290,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:52:01.000Z","msg":"100%"},{"pid":"b78e1448543000a806dc64cea34b74024a0a4258","tid":1641290,"uid":48577,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"我試過奶奶下 奶到d白色液體<br />\n吞左先發現原來係上一手中出完未清乾淨d精來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6508192dea9c20b423a01ea02b3a3c1f2102a2","tid":1641290,"uid":152